=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/wordpressbcn/events/239426032/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hardening WordPress like a Hacker con Chema Alonso</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>Barcelona</strong> &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/Barcelona-WooCommerce-Meetup/events/239503985/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WPML support desk representative Yvette Oliveau, will give presentation</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>Tarragaona</strong> &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/wordpresstarragona/events/239932101/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Diferencias entre WordPress.COM y WordPress.ORG</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>Málaga</strong> &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/WordPress-Malaga/events/240079531/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Comercio electrónico en WordPress con WooCommerce (Taller)</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>Valladolid</strong> &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/Valladolid-WordPress-Meetup/events/240114536/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WPO + RENDIMIENTO en WordPress por Rober y Rubén</a></li>\n<li>26/05 &#8211; <strong>Irún</strong> &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/Irun-WordPress-Meetup/events/239588904/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Presentación del grupo de Irun WordPress Meetup</a> (<em>Enhorabuena organizadores por vuestra 1er Meetup <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.2.5/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.2.5/72x72/1f38a.png\" alt=\"🎊\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></em>)</li>\n<li>27/05 &#8211; <strong>Almería</strong> &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/WPAlmeria/events/238862277/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Aniversario WordPress</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Fotos de las Meetups de la semana anterior</h3>\n<a